{"type": "article", "id": 23854, "title": "总有些美好而无用的东西，来自这种宅男发明家", "description": "友情提醒，前方高能", "date": "2016-03-15T19:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 50, "name": "日本"}, {"id": 6354, "name": "自拍杆"}, {"id": 24880, "name": "发明家"}, {"id": 5116, "name": "假肢"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 14, "praise_count": 127, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607141106faz9JGAQEZ6RWm1v.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>自拍杆是很多游客的必需品，但它多少会令人感到尴尬，自拍杆伤人的事件也时有发生。从去年起，意大利<a href=\"http://archeoroma.beniculturali.it/en/archaeological-site/colosseum\">罗马竞技场</a>、法国<a href=\"http://en.chateauversailles.fr/homepage\">凡尔赛宫</a>和澳大利亚<a href=\"http://www.australia.gov.au/about-australia/australian-story/sydney-opera-house\">悉尼歌剧院</a>纷纷发布了自拍杆禁令。随后迪士尼也禁止游客携带自拍杆入园。莫斯科政府甚至展开过一项<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/13332.html\">宣传活动，让人们认识到自拍是危险</a>的，甚至可能导致精神疾病（无论用不用自拍杆！）</p>\n<p>但这些禁令怎能抵挡住自拍星人的脚步啊，为了自拍，就有位日本人给自己装上了假肢。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141049rFlcQVUEYu4C86eL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">“大家好，我就是日本宅男 mansoon，今天给大家表演一下自拍。呃我的手臂格外长，请不要在意。”</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141049gaKk8bNWSrE02HoV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">感到自豪  ⁄(⁄ ⁄•⁄ω⁄•⁄ ⁄)⁄</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">这位 Mansoon 可是个狂热的宅男发明家。他设计了不少小东西，还建了个<a href=\"http://man-sooon.tumblr.com\">网站</a>把它们晒了出来。我们打算介绍比较魔性的几个。比如，呃，这个长草了的键盘：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141050ZynY5wbdJe6TM72N.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6712963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">他还晒出了制作过程：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141050F8L2Q3zy95AtKhSs.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">先去买一把草</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141051wyg8CbYSjNdtsAXH.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">做一个卡槽</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141051YgusLyGtVwcT56Wz.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141052kU0Gps5ZF9lufyL8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">大功告成，键盘长草了！</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">再比如，这个人工手指：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141052v8ld9FtIVkyTRqrA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141053Y9nx0cXE8VLsaqM5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141054KgjaCfuHMDoEXrJy.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141054OPdrlQm1Ex6hSqRN.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56166667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">（别问我它是做什么的！）</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141055Np8RAlbIqC6LuBe2.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56166667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141056DFeEy7H8vNar9KVl.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56166667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">还有这款 Windows 95 实体垃圾箱：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141057LPXQ4w3T5VAf0azy.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141058AQge97w1fnRUYdWi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">先做出大致的轮廓</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141059djZbtH6nBfvicrum.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">喷漆上色（看来不止做了一个）</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141059icAMIBjYXuLV17KG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141100yYRS42WMvKhpuwFd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">上 LOGO</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141100rptau4I0ZLmNFnMx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141101EKUpbRge9QnkmrWN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">大功告成！</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">再比如这个桌上迷你回转寿司：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141101s0KOfjTPJHoeNnlI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">看起来平淡无奇是吧</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071411010tWd7FPBw1gU2mcT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">这个也没啥意思</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141102eE1YlBAMuHDI35qf.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56181818\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">哦哈哈哈哈！</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141102sELFcnkwAer9BzSx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">看看制作过程吧</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141103VR8GBYNyJonX5Oe6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071411033vH24XYNhqEdWVKA.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56181818\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141104Mbn7vUOT3Iwfqsdk.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141105oENva1j2hD5VYdLy.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">这才是回转寿司的真正奥义</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">其他发明诸如：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141105qVwMAcxk8azGOgIh.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">动物罐</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141105qfZxT2mE5Gv7uQVK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">儿童车</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">或许这就是传说中的，“自宅成才”吧。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071411067Q1Iq3cEwSa5ybZJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.746\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.spoon-tamago.com/2016/03/12/japanese-selfie-arms/\">spoon-tamago</a><br></p>\n\n\n\n"}